properties.Name: ExperianPaymentAndLegalFilingsSummary
properties.Description: Experian payment and legal filings summary.

Columns.Name: ExperianFileNumber
Columns.Description: The unique and persistent number that identifies and tracks the Experian company.

Columns.Name: ProfileTimestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp of the Experian profile.

Columns.Name: CurrentDbt
Columns.Description: The current DBT number.

Columns.Name: PredictedDbt
Columns.Description: The company's predicted DBT.

Columns.Name: PredictedDbtDate
Columns.Description: The 'as of' date or reported date of the predicted DBT.

Columns.Name: MonthlyAverageDbt
Columns.Description: The company monthly average DBT.

Columns.Name: HighestDbtPrevious6Months
Columns.Description: The highest DBT for the company for the previous 6 months.

Columns.Name: HighestDbtPrevious5Quarters
Columns.Description: The highest DBT for the previous 5 quarters.

Columns.Name: PaymentTrendIndicationStatement
AllIndustryDbtNumber
Columns.Description: The industry DBT number.

Columns.Name: SameIndustryDbtNumber
Columns.Description: The DBT for the same industry.

Columns.Name: IndustryPaymentComparisonStatement
Columns.Description:
A statement regarding the company versus the industry regarding payments.

Ex:
"...Has paid sooner than 50% of similar businesses ..."

Columns.Name: TotalTradeAndCollectionAmount
Columns.Description: The total company trade and collections amount.

Columns.Name: AllTradesAmount
Columns.Description: The total trades amount.

Columns.Name: AllCollectionsAmount
Columns.Description: The total of all collections in process.

Columns.Name: ContinuousTradeAmount
Columns.Description: The continuous trades amount.

Columns.Name: 6MonthMinimumTradeAverageAmount
Columns.Description: The minimum trade average amount for the previous 6 months.

Columns.Name: 6MonthMaximumTradeAverageAmount
Columns.Description: The maximum trade average amount for the previous 6 months.

Columns.Name: HighestCreditAmountExtended
Columns.Description: The highest credit amount extended to the company.

Columns.Name: MostFrequentIndustryPurchasingTermsStatement
InBankruptcyIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates the company is in bankruptcy.

Columns.Name: NumberOfTaxLienFilings
Columns.Description: The number of tax lien filings.

Columns.Name: NumberOfJudgmentFilings
Columns.Description: The number of company judgment filings.

Columns.Name: SumOfLegalFilingsAmount
Columns.Description: The sum of legal filing.

Columns.Name: NumberOfUccFilings
Columns.Description: The number of UCC filings.

Columns.Name: CautionaryUccFilingsExistIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates that cautionary UCC filings exist.

Properties.Description: Experian payment and legal filings summary.
